# Atlassian Rovo MCP Server
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LOCAL DEV: OAuth 2.1 (default) — no env vars needed.
#   The MCP server at https://mcp.atlassian.com/v1/mcp uses browser-based OAuth.
#   Just reload VS Code and approve the consent flow.
#
# CI / HEADLESS: API token auth — requires org admin to enable.
#   See: https://support.atlassian.com/atlassian-rovo-mcp-server/docs/configuring-authentication-via-api-token/
#
# export ATLASSIAN_SITE_URL="https://yoursite.atlassian.net"
# export ATLASSIAN_USER_EMAIL="you@example.com"
# export ATLASSIAN_API_TOKEN="your-rovo-mcp-scoped-token-here"
